<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pricing - VibeNote.studio</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topnav">
  <a href="/dashboard" class="topnav-logo" style="text-decoration:none">&larr; VibeNote<span>.studio</span></a>
  <div class="topnav-right">
    <span class="badge badge-<%= agency.plan %>"><%= agency.plan %></span>
    <div class="agency-avatar"><%= agency.name.charAt(0).toUpperCase() %></div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="plans-page" style="max-width:1100px">
  <div class="plans-header">
    <h1>Agency pricing for small client website delivery</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-dim);font-size:14px">Per-site yearly pricing for agencies handling landing pages, brochure websites, small business websites, and portfolio websites.</p>
  </div>

  <% if (reason === 'nocredits') { %>
  <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-bottom:28px;max-width:760px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">
    You've used all currently available site slots. Move to a bigger agency plan to deliver more client websites.
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="plans-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="plan-card">
      <div class="plan-name">FTP Export Plan</div>
      <div class="plan-price">&#8377;2,000</div>
      <div class="plan-cycle">per site / year</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Generate website</li>
        <li>Unlimited edits</li>
        <li>Download full HTML CSS JS</li>
        <li>FTP deploy to client hosting</li>
        <li>Access for 1 year</li>
      </ul>
      <button class="btn btn-outline btn-block" onclick="subscribePlan('starter', '<%= plans.starter.planId %>')">Choose FTP Export</button>
    </div>

    <div class="plan-card popular">
      <div class="plan-name">Hosted Deploy Plan</div>
      <div class="plan-price">&#8377;4,500</div>
      <div class="plan-cycle">per site / year</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Generate website</li>
        <li>Unlimited edits</li>
        <li>One click deploy</li>
        <li>VibeNote hosting</li>
        <li>Free SSL</li>
        <li>Custom domain support</li>
        <li>1 year hosting</li>
      </ul>
      <button class="btn btn-gold btn-block" onclick="subscribePlan('growth', '<%= plans.growth.planId %>')">Choose Hosted Deploy</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:28px">
    <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px">Agency packs</h2>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim)">Built for agencies delivering multiple client websites every year.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted)">Typical client fee: &#8377;15,000 to &#8377;40,000</div>
    </div>

    <div class="plans-grid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);margin-top:20px">
      <div class="plan-card">
        <div class="plan-name">10 sites pack</div>
        <div class="plan-price">&#8377;35,000</div>
        <div class="plan-cycle">per year</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>For recurring small client website work</li>
          <li>Ideal for active agencies</li>
          <li>Great fit for brochure and landing page delivery</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-block" onclick="subscribePlan('growth', '<%= plans.growth.planId %>')">Choose 10 Sites Pack</button>
      </div>

      <div class="plan-card">
        <div class="plan-name">50 sites pack</div>
        <div class="plan-price">&#8377;1,50,000</div>
        <div class="plan-cycle">per year</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>For agencies using VibeNote as a delivery system</li>
          <li>Supports high-volume client website output</li>
          <li>Best economics for bulk delivery</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn btn-outline btn-block" onclick="subscribePlan('agency', '<%= plans.agency.planId %>')">Choose 50 Sites Pack</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="margin-top:24px">
    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin-bottom:8px">Typical agency math</h2>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-dim)">If the client pays &#8377;15,000 to &#8377;40,000 and your VibeNote Hosted Deploy cost is &#8377;4,500, your agency keeps the rest as profit.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://checkout.razorpay.com/v1/checkout.js"></script>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
